1
00:00:19,359 --> 00:00:20,000
Have some water.

2
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:24,359
How are you feeling?

3
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:27,679
A bit better.

4
00:00:28,359 --> 00:00:28,719
Okay.

5
00:00:29,559 --> 00:00:31,359
Make sure you get some rest these next few days.

6
00:00:34,039 --> 00:00:34,679
Daddy!

7
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:38,159
What are you doing here?

8
00:00:39,079 --> 00:00:39,520
Yixin.

9
00:00:40,159 --> 00:00:40,759
Come here.

10
00:00:43,679 --> 00:00:45,679
You two know each other?

11
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:48,880
Of course, she's my...

12
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:49,520
sister.

13
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:52,200
Sister?

14
00:00:57,079 --> 00:00:58,439
She's met me twice,

15
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:00,119
and both times called me Daddy.

16
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,520
Besides,

17
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:03,880
the name Yixin...

18
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,280
Is she really your sister?

19
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:09,400
Yes.

20
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,319
You were locked up for four years.

21
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,760
Is it that strange I have a three-year-old sister?

22
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:18,920
Kids don't know any better, so they just call people whatever.

23
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:21,159
Yixin, you can't call him that anymore.

24
00:01:21,159 --> 00:01:21,920
Understand?

25
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,400
He's not your daddy.

26
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:24,760
Okay.

27
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:28,560
Director Ren, are you making rounds or...?

28
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,680
I'm not the director anymore.

29
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:33,439
Well, if you're fine,

30
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,920
then I'll head back.

31
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:46,640
Yixin.

32
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:50,239
Have you really met him twice?

33
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,239
Yes.

34
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:55,159
The first time, Daddy picked up my ball.

35
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:57,760
The second time, Junjun bullied me,

36
00:01:58,079 --> 00:01:59,760
and Daddy saved me.

37
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,680
Daddy's so amazing!

38
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:04,760
He knocked down Junjun's dad in one go.

39
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:07,560
Daddy is obviously Daddy.

40
00:02:07,879 --> 00:02:10,759
Why won't Ruo Jin let me call him Daddy?

41
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:15,280
Inmate Ren Feifan has refused this visit.

42
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:19,039
You can write or book another visit.

43
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,759
But he'll have to agree.

44
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:29,439
He still won't forgive me?

45
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:44,919
The inmate still refuses to see you.

46
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:11,439
Why did Mommy say she's my sister?

47
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:14,520
Aren't sisters younger than moms?

48
00:04:00,159 --> 00:04:01,240
Why are you following me?

49
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,400
Why are you following me?

50
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,960
I saw you at Premier Medical Hall and the hospital.

51
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,960
Good memory.

52
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,479
Hi, I'm Su Qing.

53
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:14,759
A reporter for Beishi Daily.

54
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,240
Answer my question.

55
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,319
I was investigating something.

56
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:21,240
I thought it involved you.

57
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:22,959
But then I realized...

58
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:24,560
it didn't.

59
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,040
Then why are you still following me?

60
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,399
Don't let the family near the body.

61
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,600
One quick look from afar at the hospital morgue,

62
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,399
then rush it to the funeral home.

63
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:37,560
Remember, keep the family away from the body.

64
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,319
One quick look from afar, then off to the funeral home.

65
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,480
That's Li Xiande.

66
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,000
Yes.

67
00:04:43,199 --> 00:04:45,680
A year ago, a patient's family came to me.

68
00:04:45,839 --> 00:04:48,600
Said his son died during Li Xiande's emergency care.

69
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,680
He wanted answers from the hospital,

70
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:52,439
but was blocked from all sides,

71
00:04:52,439 --> 00:04:53,439
pressured to drop it.

72
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,199
First they offered him a fortune,

73
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,399
then came the violent threats.

74
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:58,959
The Wang Family did it.

75
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,120
So...

76
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:02,920
you also think they're illegally trafficking organs?

77
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:06,480
Where are you going?

78
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,160
To examine the body.

79
00:05:41,399 --> 00:05:43,680
Yesterday, Li Xiande had a patient who died during emergency care.

80
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:45,240
What's his name?

81
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:46,800
Wang Dong.

82
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:51,560
He's right here.

83
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,839
Why aren't there any signs of him being cut open

84
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:03,120
to have his organs removed?

85
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:15,519
Give me a hand.

86
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:35,839
What is this?

87
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,959
Drug residue. Highly toxic.

88
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:41,600
You mean he was poisoned to death?

89
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:53,600
Shh.

90
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:55,439
Are you okay?

91
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,759
You're soaked.

92
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:01,600
Let's go.

93
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,680
Good thing I just misheard.

94
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,240
Noises in the middle of the night are terrifying.

95
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:31,720
Let's go.

96
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:42,600
Dazhuang.

97
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,040
Put this on first.

98
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:49,800
Here.

99
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:52,480
Master.

100
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,519
What's going on here?

101
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:54,639
Don't get the wrong idea.

102
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:57,399
This is Su Qing, a reporter for Beishi Daily.

103
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,480
Hello, nice to meet you.

104
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,839
What's the situation inside?

105
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:06,199
Based on my prior investigation,

106
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:08,759
there should be an experimental base inside this hospital.

107
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:11,839
I suspect they're using ER patients

108
00:08:12,319 --> 00:08:13,560
for human experimentation.

109
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,959
That's outrageous!

110
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:16,680
Actually experimenting on human beings!

111
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:20,279
You're saying this hospital isn't trafficking organs,

112
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:22,160
but conducting some kind of experiment?

113
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:22,800
Yeah.

114
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:25,120
Truly, hell is empty,

115
00:08:25,399 --> 00:08:26,560
and all the devils are here.

116
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:03,159
How are things between you two lately?

117
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:08,679
Last time we went to Lijia Village together,

118
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:10,480
I feel like he

119
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,879
seems to

120
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,320
still be interested in you.

121
00:11:17,639 --> 00:11:19,720
I don't know if he's interested.

122
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,600
That hurts!

123
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:29,919
How boring.

124
00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:36,440
What's your relationship with Ren Feifan?

125
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,840
We're just colleagues.

126
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:38,799
What about you?

127
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,200
What's your relationship with him?

128
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:40,919
I...

129
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:45,480
Let me tell you,

130
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,399
Ren Feifan has a wife and child.

131
00:11:49,320 --> 00:11:51,080
You'd better not keep hanging around him...

132
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:51,840
Sorry about that.

133
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,120
She's got the wrong person.

134
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:56,279
She's an obsessed fan of Dr. Ren's.

135
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,200
Seems like she didn't get the wrong person.

136
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:04,120
And who exactly are you?

137
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,399
Me?

138
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,960
Who am I?

139
00:12:12,279 --> 00:12:13,080
Who am I?

140
00:12:13,799 --> 00:12:14,440
Stop asking.

141
00:12:14,879 --> 00:12:15,759
Just stop asking.

142
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:16,879
Please stop asking.

143
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:17,960
Calm down.

144
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,080
Let's go, let's go.

145
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,159
Lunatics.

146
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:41,000
The most likely place is right here.

147
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,200
Dazhuang,

148
00:12:42,919 --> 00:12:44,720
this time you'll pose as a myocarditis patient.

149
00:12:45,039 --> 00:12:47,120
I'll apply needles to seal your meridians.

150
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:48,320
You'll feel dizzy,

151
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:51,720
and anemia will leave your limbs weak and face pale.

152
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,399
Remember, don't get worked up.

153
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,200
Breathe slowly.

154
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,080
No problem.

155
00:12:56,279 --> 00:12:58,320
Remember, whether we succeed or not,

156
00:12:58,799 --> 00:13:00,360
you must ensure your own safety.

157
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:02,000
Our goal this time is to scout the way.

158
00:13:02,399 --> 00:13:04,679
Once you find the main gate, come right back.

159
00:13:04,919 --> 00:13:05,440
Got it?

160
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:06,440
Got it.

161
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:08,840
And take this.

162
00:13:09,159 --> 00:13:09,960
What's this?

163
00:13:09,960 --> 00:13:11,320
It's a hidden camera.

164
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,320
Blink twice and it starts recording.

165
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:15,679
Close your eyes for over 30 seconds to turn it off.

166
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,519
Understood?

167
00:13:16,759 --> 00:13:17,399
Understood.

168
00:13:18,399 --> 00:13:19,279
Let's do this, Master.
